{"tid":651421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［刑事偵緝檔案］失竊案女童疑被父親虐打","createTime":"2018-05-03T05:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T06:11:23.000Z","uid":13745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6ee2c5eea493b5c88387183b2bcb8644415f0756","tid":651421,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:51:12.000Z","msg":"500萬元鑽飾離奇失竊案，被捕後獲准保釋的10歲女童，被社工發現手腳有瘀傷，懷疑今年4月因家事問題，被父親以衣架襲擊，案件暫列作「對所看管兒童或少年人虐待或忽略」 。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，接獲社工昨日（2日）報案指，發現女童手腳有瘀傷，於是通知警方，警方初步調查，懷疑女童於今年4月，因家事問題被父親用衣架襲擊，警方安排女童送院檢查，案件暫列對所看管兒童或少年人虐待或忽略，交由黃大仙警區重案組第2隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n案件始於本周一（4月30日）晚，一名39歲姓李女子報警，聲稱被人偷走放在黃大仙下邨龍滿樓一個單位、共值約500萬元的鑽石頸鏈以及鑽石手鐲。據了解，女事主與男戶主報稱朋友關係。李已婚，早前與丈夫不和分開，及後到男戶主位於黃大仙下邨龍滿樓的家中居住，惟不受男戶主女兒喜歡，經常與女童發生爭執，其鑽飾疑被女童暗中棄掉。<br />\n<br />\n女童起初表示，將鑽石鏈拋出窗外；其後又指未有將鑽飾丟掉，暗中藏起來，但拒絕提供收藏地點；及後再三查問，女童又聲稱將鑽飾交給一名12歲女同學，警方派員到該女同學家中，該同學稱未有接收過東西，警員經搜查後未有發現。<br />\n<br />\n警方經調查後，先後拘捕男戶主10歲女兒及2名12歲同學，涉嫌盜竊，其中一名12歲女童已無條件獲釋，另外2名女童亦已獲准保釋。有關首飾仍未起回。<br />\n召喚大勇義仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1b0b6ea5bafc474a7a075e9cdf5cd21d8db204","tid":651421,"uid":63845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:52:24.000Z","msg":"冇左條大水喉，梗係打到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a2c17e54042c87fd6e92b5e9e79dde83dcf727","tid":651421,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:52:51.000Z","msg":"案中案中案"},{"pid":"c6fde3ba3aa99faa0072a522ac3304126f0cd83c","tid":651421,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:54:22.000Z","msg":"好想睇條女咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5192cc8520081720896d27375ac4391871e10216","tid":651421,"uid":13745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=V_QR3a5MOuU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DV_QR3a5MOuU&d=v%2F4OAN7oD4ab9BaYZu%2Bh68PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ad1aab7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=V_QR3a5MOuU</a><br />\n刑事偵緝檔案2片尾曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n愛 何以竟找到我<br />\n在剎那間發生好比暗裡閃過的火<br />\n你 從我心中經過<br />\n讓我徹底無助 真的叫我非愛不可<br />\n願伴著你 就是沒自我<br />\n亦未問為什麼 願永遠瘋魔<br />\n就是在玩弄我 亦自願受著過錯<br />\n道別話未說 亦盡量去拖<br />\n呈獻出一切去求你這一晚陪伴我<br />\n只需當打發時間別疑慮太多<br />\n留住這一個夜晚在明日重播<br />\n陪伴我一世是這首愛的輓歌<br />\n世間一切也無法去抵抗時日過<br />\n不管真心跟瞞騙亦同樣結果<br />\n來吧再一次被你欺騙未為過<br />\n明日我一個夜裡再哼這首輓歌<br />\n想得很清楚 真愛難負荷<br />\n需要痛苦都太多<br />\n今宵可不可 無須要太清楚<br />\n只要剎那間結果<br />\n若是玩弄我 唯求並未揭破<br />\n願承認我是很傻<br />\n願熱烈渡過 夢幻內渡過<br />\n未計較終會留下我<br />\n想得很清楚 真愛難負荷<br />\n需要痛苦都太多<br />\n今宵可不可 無須要太清楚<br />\n只要剎那間結果<br />\n若是玩弄我 唯求並未揭破<br />\n願承認我是很傻<br />\n願熱烈渡過 夢幻內渡過<br />\n未計較終會留下我"},{"pid":"9a4439f35d0f9ef018c76e79a3f659cdb6d87815","tid":651421,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6fde3ba3aa99faa0072a522ac3304126f0cd83c","tid":651421,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:54:22.000Z","msg":"好想睇條女咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:06:09.000Z","msg":"10歲定35歲個件先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df96df685754c25b934797537d1d564ef5f22221","tid":651421,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a4439f35d0f9ef018c76e79a3f659cdb6d87815","tid":651421,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6fde3ba3aa99faa0072a522ac3304126f0cd83c","tid":651421,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:54:22.000Z","msg":"好想睇條女咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:06:09.000Z","msg":"10歲定35歲個件先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:08:36.000Z","msg":"人妻"},{"pid":"4ca92a31737277f82e8c84937371f1023027c47b","tid":651421,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180503/large/03la2p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180503%2Flarge%2F03la2p10.jpg&h=2d122f1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43e0b3ae5d60845e445e96d8715bbce822714fa5","tid":651421,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ca92a31737277f82e8c84937371f1023027c47b","tid":651421,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180503/large/03la2p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180503%2Flarge%2F03la2p10.jpg&h=2d122f1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}